# Buttons & Actions Pattern Guide

Interactive element patterns using the established Button component system.

## Basic Button Usage

```tsx
import { Button } from "~/components/Button";

// Basic button modes
<Button mode="primary">Primary Action</Button>
<Button mode="secondary">Secondary Action</Button>
<Button mode="action">Special Action</Button>
<Button mode="creative">Creative Action</Button>
<Button mode="destructive">Delete Action</Button>
```

## Button with Loading States

```tsx
import { useNavigation } from "react-router";

export default function FormPage() {
  const navigation = useNavigation();
  
  return (
    <Button
      mode="primary"
      type="submit"
      loading={navigation.state === "submitting"}
    >
      Save Changes
    </Button>
  );
}
```

